messages.content: Your goal is to report the percent of Microsoft year-to-date stock price change. To do that, go to the website finance.yahoo.com. At the top of the page, you will find a search bar.Enter the value 'MSFT', to get information about the Microsoft stock price.At the top of the resulting page you will see a default chart of Microsoft stock price.Click on 'YTD' at the top of that chart, and report the percent value that shows up just below it.

text.value: The Year-To-Date (YTD) percentage change for Microsoft stock (MSFT) is 23.41%.

browser_automation.input: Go to https://finance.yahoo.com, enter 'MSFT' in the search bar, and on the resulting Microsoft stock page, click on 'YTD' at the top of the stock chart. Report the percent value that appears below the chart.
browser_automation.output: Successfully obtained the Year-To-Date percentage change for Microsoft stock (MSFT) from Yahoo Finance. The YTD percentage is 23.41%.
